gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.calculation

Class SignedResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.calculation.SignedResult

  • public final class SignedResult
extends java.lang.Object

    Represents a signed, totally-immutable calculation result.

    This class is similar to CalculationResult but stores only primitive values and is suitable for storing in a database.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
